LABEL: Place of birth
RULE:
MATCH (a3)<--(a2)<--(a1)<--(a0)<--(b)-->(c0)-->(c1)
WHERE a3.VALUE='Place of birth' AND a3.PATH='/HTML/BODY/TABLE/TBODY/TR/TD/TABLE/TBODY/TR/TD/DIV/TABLE/TBODY/TR/TD/SPAN/STRONG/text()' AND a3.POSITION='1' 
AND a2.VALUE='STRONG' AND a2.POSITION='1' 
AND a1.VALUE='SPAN' AND a1.POSITION='1' 
AND a0.VALUE='TD' AND a0.POSITION='1' 
AND b.VALUE='TR' 
AND c0.VALUE='TD' AND c0.POSITION='2' 
AND c1.NODE_TYPE='3' AND c1.POSITION='1' 
 RETURN c1.VALUE AS VALUE, c1.URL AS URL, 'Template' in LABELS(c1) as template
